o Tutorical make their profiles stand out.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nTo make things better, external reviews work seamlessly with the <a title=\"Import your Acadam and UniversityTutor Profiles\" href=\"http://tutorical.com/blog/meta/import-your-acadam-and-universitytutor-profiles\">Tutorical Importer</a>. All reviews imported from a UniversityTutor or Acadam profile are automatically added to your External Reviews.', 'External Reviews', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '132-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-06 17:03:39', '2013-09-06 17:03:39', '', 132, 'http://tutorical.com/blog/meta/132-autosave-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
